<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>BurgerCraze | Delicious Fast Food</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* --- Reset & Global Styles --- */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }

        :root {
            --primary-color: #ff4757;
            --secondary-color: #ffa502;
            --dark-color: #2f3542;
            --light-bg: #f1f2f6;
            --white: #ffffff;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--white);
            color: var(--dark-color);
        }

        /* --- Navbar Styles --- */
        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px 8%;
            background-color: var(--white);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--dark-color);
        }

        .logo span {
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        .nav-links {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
        }

        .nav-links li {
            margin: 0 20px;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--dark-color);
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover, .nav-links a.active {
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        .btn-order {
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-order:hover {
            background-color: #e03d4b;
        }

        /* --- Hero Section --- */
        .hero {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 60px 8%;
            background-color: var(--light-bg);
            min-height: calc(85vh - 80px);
        }

        .hero-content {
            max-width: 50%;
        }

        .hero-content h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .hero-content h1 span {
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        .hero-content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #57606f;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .hero-buttons a {
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-right: 15px;
            display: inline-block;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: var(--white);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #e03d4b;
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background-color: transparent;
            border: 2px solid var(--dark-color);
            color: var(--dark-color);
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background-color: var(--dark-color);
            color: var(--white);
        }

        .hero-image img {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 500px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        /* --- Menu Section --- */
        .menu-section {
            padding: 80px 8%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .menu-section h2 {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .menu-section h2 span {
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        .section-subtitle {
            color: #747d8c;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .menu-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .menu-card {
            background-color: var(--white);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            text-align: left;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .menu-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .menu-card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .menu-card h3 {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .menu-card p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #747d8c;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .card-footer {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: auto;
        }

        .price {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        .btn-add {
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
            border: none;
            color: var(--white);
            width: 35px;
            height: 35px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            font-size: 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-add:hover {
            background-color: #e69500;
        }

        /* --- Footer --- */
        footer {
            background-color: var(--dark-color);
            color: var(--white);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        /* --- Responsive Adjustments --- */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .navbar {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 15px;
            }
            
            .hero {
                flex-direction: column-reverse;
                text-align: center;
                gap: 30px;
            }

            .hero-content {
                max-width: 100%;
            }

            .hero-content h1 {
                font-size: 36px;
            }

            .hero-buttons a {
                margin: 5px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header class="navbar">
        <div class="logo">Burger<span>Craze</span></div>
        <nav>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="#" class="active">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Menu</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">About Us</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
        <a href="#" class="btn-order">Order Now</a>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Satisfy Your <br><span>Craving</span> Instantly</h1>
            <p>Made with 100% fresh ingredients, sizzling hot, and delivered right to your doorstep in minutes.</p>
            <div class="hero-buttons">
                <a href="#" class="btn-primary">Explore Menu</a>
                <a href="#" class="btn-secondary">View Offers</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-image">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1568901346375-23c9450c58cd?q=80&w=600&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Delicious Burger">
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="menu-section">
        <h2>Our <span>Popular</span> Dishes</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Check out our absolute crowd favorites</p>
        
        <div class="menu-grid">
            <div class="menu-card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1568901346375-23c9450c58cd?q=80&w=400&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Classic Burger">
                <h3>Classic Cheesy Burger</h3>
                <p>Juicy beef patty, cheddar cheese, lettuce, and secret sauce.</p>
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <span class="price">$8.99</span>
                    <button class="btn-add">+</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="menu-card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1513104890138-7c749659a591?q=80&w=400&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Pizza">
                <h3>Pepperoni Feast</h3>
                <p>Fresh mozzarella, loads of pepperoni, and Italian herbs.</p>
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <span class="price">$12.49</span>
                    <button class="btn-add">+</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="menu-card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573080496219-bb080dd4f877?q=80&w=400&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="French Fries">
                <h3>Peri-Peri Crispy Fries</h3>
                <p>Golden crisp fries tossed in spicy peri-peri seasoning.</p>
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <span class="price">$4.99</span>
                    <button class="btn-add">+</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 BurgerCraze. All rights reserved. Built for food lovers.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
